

1. Get the real domains
   - Ask customer for prod, staging, localhost domains
   - Add all to allowedDomains

2. Generate API key + namespace  
   - apiKey: random string, e.g. acme_7f3k9p
   - namespace: lowercase, no spaces

3. Review config JSON
   - protectedRoutes match their pages
   - vault routes have valid video URLs
   - webhookUrl points to Railway
   - timing values make sense

4. Onboard via Postman
   - POST /admin/onboard-company with JSON
   - Check response: { "status": "company_onboarded" }
   - GET /shield/config with x-api-key to verify

5. Verify in admin dashboard
   - Check /admin/companies for new company
   - Check backend logs for errors

6. Hand off to customer
   - API key
   - Script tag: <script src="https://your-domain.com/shield.js" data-api-key="key"></script>
   - Dashboard URL

7. Security check
   - Lock /admin/companies with basic auth
   - Remove localhost from allowedDomains on prod
